content: Diving deep into time series analysis for the AI trading algo. The more I learn, the more I realize how much there is to know 📚
Had a setback - the bot didn’t perform well with real-time data. But setbacks are just setups for comebacks, right? Time to refine and recalibrate. ⚙️
Just posted a new video breaking down the setback with the trading bot. Transparency pays off - got some great feedback and ideas from the community! 📈
Met up with a new contact from the trading meetup. They shared some killer insights on risk management. Implementing these could really change the game for my bot 🔒
Big win! Got an offer from the quant firm in London! It's not a full-time position yet, but it's a start. Time to level up my international market game 🌍
Revamping my LinkedIn profile to reflect my new international market insights. Also added my latest YouTube video on risk management. Networking and branding in full swing! 📝
The AI bot's performing better with real-time data now. Not perfect, but progress. Sometimes it's the small wins that keep you going 💪
Caught up with my mentor again. We discussed how AI can democratize trading but also questioned the ethics of high-frequency trading. Deep stuff to ponder 🤔
Just had a call with the London firm. They're impressed with my progress and want me to focus on a project that could lead to a full-time role. Time to buckle down! 🌟
The project with the London firm is intense but rewarding. It's all about creating a sustainable AI-driven trading strategy. Learning so much about long-term market trends 📊
Had a setback - one of my mentors got a new job and won't be available as much. It's a loss, but it's also a chance to lean on my other connections more.
Just uploaded a video discussing how algorithms balance speed and fairness in trading. It's about time we reflect on what markets should reward. 🤔
The AI trading bot is now integrating real-time data with better accuracy. It's like tuning a piano - precision is everything. 🎹

Had an interesting conversation with a colleague about the societal implications of AI urban planning. It's not just about optimization—it's about creating cities that prioritize sustainability and equality. 🌍

Just got an email from the London firm - they're excited about my project progress. They're considering me for a full-time position. If cognitive tech can outperform humans in trading, does it democratize opportunity or reinforce control? 🤔
